<h3 class="center" style="font-size: 30px;"><u>Poem For You:</u></h3>
<table>
    <th class="center">
        <p style="font-size: 20px; color: red;">
            On this day of love so true,<br>
            I give my heart and soul to you.<br>
            Like the stars that light the night,<br>
            You make my world shine warm and bright.<br>
            <br>
            Your laughter sings a melody,<br>
            A tune that sets my spirit free.<br>
            With every glance, with every touch,<br>
            I fall again—I love you much.<br>
            <br>
            Through storm and calm, through joy and pain,<br>
            I'll stand beside you in the rain.<br>
            For every heartbeat, every sigh,<br>
            You're my forever, my reason why.<br>
            
            So take my hand, let's dance through time,<br>
            With love so endless, pure, divine.<br>
            No words could ever quite convey,<br>
            How much you mean—Happy Valentine's Day. </p>
